<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id748e3266-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7" identifier="/us/usc/t36/s120110"><num value="120110">§ 120110.</num><heading> Liability for acts of officers and agents</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The corporation is liable for any act of any officer or agent of the corporation acting within the scope of the authority of the corporation.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id748e3267-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/110/254/s1/a/2">Pub. L. 110–254, § 1(a)(2)</ref>, <date date="2008-06-30">June 30, 2008</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/122/2421">122 Stat. 2421</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
